Comment: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:10.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:19.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:28.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:35.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:40.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:55.26,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:04:00.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:10.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:14.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:24.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:32.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
